{"title":"水手王百连","authors":["王亚平"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":6,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手王百连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王亚平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年六月三十日夜晚，我刘邓大军四十万胜利地渡过了黄河，当时有三百名水手，配合我人民解放大军英勇地划着大小木船，最速的只五分钟就抢渡过黄河，时隔两年的今日，特写此诗，以纪念这位水上英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手王百连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住在黄河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在河里打鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在河边种田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他生在河边六十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水浪头大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪头冲上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在浪里浮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船在浪里转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的老水手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕风，不怕浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在浪里驾小船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘邓大军过黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一九四七年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队访问老水手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访到水上英雄王百连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“别看风浪大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫怕黄水险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾船过黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一袋旱烟吸不完”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士敬他酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸他有经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来四乡水手们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请他来训练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“这任务我承担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把蒋匪军打到南天边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们日子才平安”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里，星星刚出现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手到河湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木船抛下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上试小船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士热心来学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上船架机枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上船运子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手三百名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大军四十万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强渡黄河下中原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边树木多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树下藏木船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声命令过黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大船小船都出现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月在空中照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪炮运上船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士报名打冲锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手争渡第一船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水手王百连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划动第一船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱光膀子摇大桨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船开好似一只箭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁风行，穿大浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破敌人火力网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士齐欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪炮震天响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划的快，走的稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡过一船又一船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎了蒋匪军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉还乡团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气打到大别山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九、六、末、北平。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}